.000Z","msg":"幾時叫埋北韓兄弟俄爹都開條熱線比香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21716f5684a76be752d48d41b65355492bd3960b","tid":2495833,"uid":338459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"其實外國人要入藉支國要咩條件? 交稅交n年或者結婚先有資格?"},{"pid":"7b7288c4b87a4aa4e08e71014a0c4be878f534c1","tid":2495833,"uid":63183,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"上回提要：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E5%8D%88%E5%AE%89.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25AE%2589.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=8b2941bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近來有好多香港人都申請移民英國同BNO簽證，英國內政部就好貼心咁設立廣東話專線，喺凌晨開工回應香港人嘅疑問。喺英國官方網站話，市民可以打電話或者寄電郵畀講廣東話嘅工作人員，詢問有關佢哋申請嘅問題，不過唔會就個人情況提供建議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5714&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=4592264f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5714</a>"},{"pid":"8ee664cead0c40d44a3830eae053976ef33ad74c","tid":2495833,"uid":33424,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"東施效颦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc12371eea27c64b7e440bee5322b90bf229c7b","tid":2495833,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:11:36.000Z","msg":"移民中國?係唔係開比非洲用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da13c2050fdc03d321580356e8bc24ce1a5f5db5","tid":2495833,"uid":225798,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"根據中國官方定義，「境外」包括港澳台及其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n被港獨了"},{"pid":"2d90d69